The body of a missing four-year-old girl was discovered at around 8pm on Wednesday night. The little girl had been raped and murdered. Her body was found discarded in a drain on Eldorado Park Extension 2‚ Soweto‚ Johannesburg. According to community members‚ the little girl was last seen in the company of a man on Wednesday afternoon. Police say the man has since been arrested. According to police reports‚ the community believes that the suspect did not act alone. This story is developing. – TimesLIVE   Source: TMG Digital.